TITLE: After 25 Years, I Still Don’t Know What To Expect From My MS

TITLE: This Is What No One Tells You About Massive Weight Loss
SUMMARY: I’ve done all the work, put in all the effort, and still, I struggle ― I still, despite my efforts to the contrary, spend more time hating my body than loving it.
